text: Thomas Mashiane (born 31 May 1996) is a South African cricketer. He made his List A debut for Northerns in the 2018–19 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge on 17 March 2019. He made his Twenty20 debut for Mpumalanga in the 2019–20 CSA Provincial T20 Cup on 13 September 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Mpumalanga cricketers Category:Northerns cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
